        {
            "title": "加拿大總理卡尼尋求與習近平會面 以緩和貿易緊張關係",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"加拿大總理卡尼尋求與習近平會面 以緩和貿易緊張關係\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uSDsNuO0rmA3C8NG4.pEnA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/48ce4c50-8e76-11f0-bcbf-3ddbb7b00142\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">加拿大總理卡尼尋求與習近平會面 以緩和貿易緊張關係</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
